  "instructions": [
    "Combine teff flour, water, and salt in a bowl and mix until smooth.",
    "Heat a non-stick skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add garlic and sauté for 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add onion and sauté for an additional 2-3 minutes, until softened.",
    "Add maitakes and sauté for 3-4 minutes, until browned.",
    "Stir in spinach and cook until wilted, about 1-2 minutes.",
    "Stir in raisins and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until they start to plump.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and top with a spoonful of melted clarified butter.",
    "If using, sprinkle with bleu cheese crumbles for an added burst of flavor.",
    "Serve the injera on the side, either toasted or untoasted, as desired."
  ],
